    {
      "name": "Standalone-Yet-Connected Aim Architecture",
      "category": "Structure",
      "description": "Each aim produces something independently valuable \u2014 a deliverable, a resolved question, or a contribution the field gains regardless of other aims. At the same time, the aim naturally points forward so the reader senses a next chapter without feeling the aim is merely setup.",
