    },
    {
      "name": "Strategic Framing of Preliminary Work & Personnel",
      "category": "Content",
      "description": "Pilot data is positioned as a feasibility gate that reveals the next necessary question \u2014 not as a highlight reel of accomplishments. Personnel are framed in terms of scientific enablement (why this question is tractable because of them) rather than credential listing.",
