          "label": "Key personnel are introduced through the scientific or methodological condition they satisfy, not through qualifications alone"
        },
        {
          "id": "no_resume_lines",
          "label": "Personnel descriptions are woven into the scientific argument rather than appearing as credential inserts"
        }
      ],
      "priority": 3
